OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA cloudy
OL,6,Fevening with outbreaks of rain.
OL,7,FStaying mostly cloudy overnight with
OL,8,Foutbreaks of rain, but a few clearer
OL,9,Fspells developing in the west. Breezy.
OL,10,
OL,11,CFriday:FArgyll mostly cloudy with
OL,12,Foccasional showers. Drier with
OL,13,Fbrighter spells from the Central Belt
OL,14,Fsouthwards by day. Showers building
OL,15,Facross the area during the evening.
OL,16,FWinds freshening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
